These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, amber, ivory, purple
House: colonial, wooden, futuristic, cape-cod
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, motorbike, snowmobile, jet-ski
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, musical, satire
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, folk, jazz, rock
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, november, april, january
4 different games are played: snooker, whist, bridge, backgammon
 1. the fan of ambient is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching adventure movies is the wooden house##1
 3. the cape-cod house is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in april is the wooden house##1
 5. the person playing bridge is between the person playing snooker and the person driving the snowmobile##2
 6. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 7. the person who likes fuchsia is the person who's birthday is in march##1
 8. the person who likes fuchsia is in an odd position##4
 9. the person watching musical movies is the person who likes amber##1
10. the person who likes ivory is in an even position##4
11. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
12. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
13. the futuristic house is on the left of the fan of rock##1
14. the cape-cod house is on the far left or far right##3
15. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1
16. the person who likes purple is in an odd position##4
17. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left or far right##3
18. the person who's birthday is in january is the person playing backgammon##1
19. the fan of folk is the colonial house##1
20. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
21. the person watching adventure movies is the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Color      | purple        | ivory   | fuchsia         | amber  |
| House          | futuristic         | wooden   | colonial   | cape-cod |
| Transport         | snowmobile | motorbike    | jet-ski | scooter   |
| Movie-Genre   | action        | adventure  | satire      | musical   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz          | rock       | folk        | ambient   |
| Birthday           | january        | april      | march    | november    |
| Game         | backgammon | bridge | snooker      | whist   |

