The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, sudoku, magic-tricks, traveling
House: cape-cod, palace, colonial, farmhouse
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, architect, teacher, photographer
 1. the person eating papaya is on the left or right of the palace house##3
 2. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the bongani-smoker##3
 3. the person who growsorchid is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the palace house##3
 5. the person eating banana is the architect##1
 6. the architect is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 7. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the teacher##3
 8. the photographer is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 9. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
10. the librarian is on the far right##1
11. the librarian is the person who growstulip##1
12. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
13. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3
14. the person drinking tea is on the left of the librarian##1
15. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the person eating plum##3
16. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
17. the person who growsdaisy is in an even position##4
18. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the photographer##1
19. the oliveros-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
20. the ritmeester-smoker is in an odd position##4
21. the person eating pumpkin is in an odd position##4

