The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, house, folk, salsa
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, may, january, october
 1. the person eating pumpkin is between the baccarat-smoker and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
 2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who growslily##1
