 8. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far right##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4
10. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3
11. the fan of house is on the left or right of the person eating apple##3
12. the person eating lemon is the person who's birthday is in february##1
13. the person who's birthday is in january is in an even position##4
14. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
15. the siglo-smoker is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
16. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
17. the person playing domino is the fan of punk##1
18. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person playing whist##1
