The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, sunflower, rose, bellflower
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, folk, soul, techno
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite, mirinda, soy-milk
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, mouse, rabbit
City: hamburg, venice, liverpool, london
 1. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
 2. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
