 7. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 8. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
 9. the person who growsbellflower is in an odd position##4
10. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
11. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
12. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
13. the person driving the taxi is in an odd position##4
14. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
15. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person traveling to liverpool##2
16. the fan of folk is between the person who growsazalea and the owner of the mouse##2
17. the person driving the ship is on the far left or far right##3
18. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1

